#: ../../C/creep.rst:5
msgid "creep"
msgstr "creep"

#: ../../C/creep.rst:7
msgid "v\\."
msgstr "動詞"

#: ../../C/creep.rst:9
msgid ""
"To advance, grow, or multiply inexorably. In hackish usage this verb has "
"overtones of menace and silliness, evoking the creeping horrors of low-"
"budget monster movies."
msgstr ""
"容赦なく前進し、増大し、または増殖すること。ハッカー流の用法では、この動詞は脅威とばかばかしさの含みを帯び、低予算のモンスター映画の這い寄る恐怖を想起させます。"
